00:21:56.370 --> 00:21:59.100 align:middle line:84%
if you're going to harvest
all the things that you

00:21:59.100 --> 00:22:02.820 align:middle line:84%
plan to harvest that you
started sowing months back.

00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:06.950 align:middle line:90%


00:22:06.950 --> 00:22:09.500 align:middle line:84%
So the idea is that
a group of people

00:22:09.500 --> 00:22:14.390 align:middle line:84%
