00:22:43.300 --> 00:22:44.500 align:middle line:90%
we can get people too.

00:22:44.500 --> 00:22:52.100 align:middle line:90%


00:22:52.100 --> 00:22:55.250 align:middle line:84%
>> As a farmer, you want
to create healthy soils,

00:22:55.250 --> 00:22:57.350 align:middle line:84%
and healthy plants,
and healthy animals.

00:22:57.350 --> 00:23:00.020 align:middle line:84%
And further up the
food chain, you

00:23:00.020 --> 00:23:04.640 align:middle line:84%
make sure that you create
the soil that invites

00:23:04.640 --> 00:23:06.170 align:middle line:90%
the right sets of microbes.

00:23:06.170 --> 00:23:11.470 align:middle line:90%


00:23:11.470 --> 00:23:17.020 align:middle line:84%
